node.text:
I made my Abuela's Berenjenas en Escabeche 🍆 (Pickled Eggplant) using my favorite jars @leparfaitworldwide 
This recipe is so easy to make and perfect for this time of the year 😋, click the link in my BIO for the recipe! 
And watch the video only on my IGTV, now!! 
💚
#pickled #eggplants #keepcookingbehappy #gabyskitchen #ad

Just Smile by LiQWYD https://soundcloud.com/liqwyd

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gaby's Kitchen on August 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
Not food, just me! Tired? You bet! Happy? Almost always! I am taking a tiny hiatus, to recharge and keep up with my 2nd book with #atkkids and get ready to launch my 1st book #foodrelatedstories 
But here are some things you might want to do while I am gone! 
There is an OUTTAKES & DELETED SCENES VIDEO #youtube for you to watch! 😉
You can also go to my BIO and: 
💚subscribe to my channel
💚sign up to receive my newsletter 
💚donate to Daniel Huerta Fundraiser 
💚pre-order my 1st book
Or turn your phone off and go for a walk!
See you soon!
#keepcookingbehappy #gabyskitchen #getorganizedforever #askgaby @gabymelian 

@patunia 💚 you are the best!
